title: #204 - Chad Goes Deep (The Party Bros)
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast we're joined by Chad & J.T. of Chad Goes Deep, aka the Party Bros! Together we discuss getting stoked, small dong pride, kindness in the face of aggression, the value of house parties, and a whole lot more!
